{
  "stem": "4184.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And after a while, I resumed-- when I went to a different home, then I found mail from my parents, where they were put into a camp in Westerbork.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they were able to write to me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So in those days, I still had heard occasionally from them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I think they were allowed to write once a month.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So-- and so we stayed in Clermont-Ferrand.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then Mr.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Barzange decided that they need to go back to their own village.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But he didn't want to take me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So he found somebody by the name of Mr.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Baer-- B-A-E-R, I think, and that he run a Jewish organization.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So he took me there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he promised this Mr.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Barzange that they would-- he would take me, and take care of me, and take me to a home, and I would be safe.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And he took me on a bus, a couple hours away from Clermont-Ferrand, in the mountains someplace.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I don't know the village or anything about it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And the people-- there were a lot of Jewish people there-- I mean, not a lot.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I would say maybe 100.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And you slept in big dormitories on cots.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And they had rationed out the food.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We had very little food-- one little piece of bread and some soup, and very little.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I noticed that people were-- every day people were going away.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I don't know where they went to.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And there were always less people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And then people started to talk.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They weren't sure where they were, and where the other people were gone.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And I remember the lady that sent me originally to the Ose home, that she was in Limoges.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And I wrote to her.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I met her in Paris.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
